# Estratégia de indexação

Exemplos de índices importantes:

```js
db.predictions.createIndex({ project_id: 1, created_at: -1 })

db.predictions.createIndex({ model_id: 1, version_id: 1 })

db.predictions.createIndex({ "prediction.label": 1 })

db.predictions.createIndex({ "feedback.is_correct": 1 })

db.alerts.createIndex({ status: 1, severity: 1 })

db.audit_events.createIndex({ project_id: 1, created_at: -1 })
```

